AD | Happiness to me is being able to inspire other women to find happiness in the simplicity of their life. Fashion is one of the main ways we express ourselves to others. Even when you’re just walking through the city and passing by people on the street or in a cafe, your outfit is saying something to them. Making sure to present myself confidently, elegantly, and positively is so important to me. The @Chopard Happy Diamond collection is another way of wearing what I feel. It’s a beautiful collection that gathers all representations of Happiness, love, and femininity. The pieces come to life as you wear them, and add spirit to any outfit! #InternationalDayOfHappiness #HappywithChopard #WhatMakesMeHappy

I’m 24! 
I know that’s not very old, but it feels so grand to me. Within my 24 years of living I am proud to say I have accomplish so many of my goals, & keeping God as the foundation of my life has allowed me to build something I am so happy with. I’m super excited to get old, to build a home, so write, to acquire new recipes, to meet new friends. There are so many amazing women that Iv look up to that are the age I am now. Whether fictional or real woman, they makes me believe I can do amazing things as they did. I’m so proud of my brand I’ve created, the life I have found in New York, and especially the people! Looking forward to many more years as my lovely little self 🤍🥂

Christmas time! 
A time to remember Jesus, His wonderful life and all He did for us out of love 🤍 He is risen and gives life to us all. I am forever grateful of my kind, loving, and wonderful king Jesus ✨
A beautiful 2023! A year full of true love, friendship, great food, Paris, many novels, new beaches, and a little grey kitten 🤍 I couldn’t ask for more, my heart is so full it thanks God everyday!
